h minor issues since the core functionality is captured. I've identified two minor issues: the OOM rationale explaining the stderr-first ordering in section 6, and ServiceAvailabilityCheckHandler missing from the hints in section 4. Overall, the knowledge file is quite solid despite these small gaps.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":16865,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":16865,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e83dbe1d-1140-45e5-a7b8-6be2103e3a9a","uuid":"aa9aa20c-1ff5-462a-8e1d-3eef60209821"}
